data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. LOCATION!  Immaculate home on an oversized corner lot.  About 1 mile to historic Dearborn Street and less than 2 miles to Manasota Key and The Englewood Beaches / Stump Pass Park!  No Flood Insurance Zone- Save $$!  This adorable home has been completely updated:  2018 Roof, New Gutters, 2022 A/C, 2023 Hot Water Heater, 2020 Garage Door, 2023 Dishwasher, new fans & fixtures, fresh paint exterior and interior.  The perimeter of the entire property has a new wooden fence which creates privacy and a backdrop for your beautiful landscaped back & front yard.  Two 2022 Sheds are strategically placed in the backyard.  Shed #1 is currently used as an Art Studio and has a walkway up to its front deck.  The Studio has a loft for additional storage and has insulated finished painted dry walls, plank flooring, electricity and a window AC unit.  Keep it as a Studio or convert is to a kid's playhouse or an adult gathering clubhouse.  Shed #2 has electricity and is used for additional storage.  To complete your backyard entertainment or relaxation, hop into the new pool which has a new pump and cover.  The back lanai is an inviting addition off the kitchen and dining room that faces your backyard oasis.  The floorplan of this home allows for privacy with a split bedroom design.  The master bedroom/ bathroom is in the front of the home. The guest bedroom and bath are on the opposite side of the living room.  Snuggle in the living room by the electric fireplace after a long day of local golfing, fishing, boating, beaching or hanging out at the many local establishments.  Live entertainment on Manasota Key, Dearborn Street, Stump Pass etc.  No deed restrictions - store your boat in your yard.  Two public boat launches within a mile from your driveway - Indian Mound State Park or the other launch is about a mile the opposite direction.  Call for your private showing today!
